た。運び屋ハヤブサジェッターが率いるスペーストラベラーズの面々もそのひとつで、謎の男ヘンリーからの依頼を受けて奇妙な荷物を運ぶことになった。スペーストラベラーズの面々に待ち受ける運命とは!?","name":"スペーストラベラーズ The Animation","name_cn":"太空游侠 动画","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"独立ova","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"空","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"太空游侠 动画"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"Space Travelers: The Animation"},{"v":"Supêsutoraberâzu: The Animation"},{"v":"极道狂热份子"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"发售日","value":"2000-06-23"},{"key":"imdb_id","value":"tt2961122"},{"key":"导演","value":"宇井孝司"},{"key":"脚本","value":"小出克彦"},{"key":"音乐","value":"渡辺俊幸"},{"key":"作画监督","value":"高橋昇、宍倉敏"},{"key":"製作","value":"フジテレビジョン、ROBOT、東映"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":5,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":3,"5":2,"6":0,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":4.4},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":4,"wish":6,"collect":8,"doing":0},"id":301352,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["日本","OVA"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"2000-06-21","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/c9/66/18826_XQNxk.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/c9/66/18826_XQNxk.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/c9/66/18826_XQNxk.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/c9/66/18826_XQNxk.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/c9/66/18826_XQNxk.jpg"},"summary":"《成人童话系列》（オトナの童話シリーズ）是根据《本当は恐ろしい童話》制作的恐怖动画，包括格林童话和日本昔话两弹。\r\n残虐性溢れる血と愛欲にみちたストーリー…。“本当は恐ろしい童話”。\r\n\r\n第1话《汉索与葛丽泰》/第2话《蓝胡子》/第3话《灰姑娘》","name":"オトナの童話シリーズI 世にも恐ろしいグリム童話","name_cn":"令人战栗的格林童话","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":34,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猎奇","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黑童话","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恐怖","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童话","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GroupTac","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000年6月","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小说改","count